column16: Omar Vizquel grounds out, pitcher Travis Schlichting to second baseman Orlando Hudson to first baseman James Loney.
Taylor Teagarden flies out to center fielder Matt Kemp.    David Murphy to 3rd.
Marlon Byrd out on a sacrifice fly to left fielder Juan Pierre.    Nelson Cruz scores.    David Murphy to 2nd.
David Murphy reaches on force attempt, fielding error by second baseman Orlando Hudson.    Nelson Cruz to 3rd.
Chase Utley walks.    Carlos Ruiz to 2nd.
Shane Victorino called out on strikes.
Greg Dobbs flies out to center fielder Matt Kemp.
Jimmy Rollins grounds out, shortstop Rafael Furcal to first baseman James Loney.
Raul Ibanez lines out to right fielder Andre Ethier.
Ryan Howard homers (17) on a fly ball to left center field.
